<span class="comment">% info: plot grid with different spacings</span>
<span class="comment">%</span>
<span class="comment">% syntax: gridManual(steps,style)</span>
<span class="comment">%</span>
<span class="comment">% input:</span>
<span class="comment">%</span>
<span class="comment">% output:</span>
<span class="comment">%</span>
<span class="comment">% example: gridManual([-20:5:20],{'Linestyle',':','Color',[1 1 1]*.5})</span>
<span class="comment">%</span>
<span class="comment">% requires:</span>
<span class="comment">%</span>
<span class="comment">% see also:</span>
<span class="comment">%</span>
<span class="comment">% created with: MATLAB ver. 8.6.0.267246 (R2015b) on Microsoft Windows 7 Professional  Version 6.1 (Build 7601: Service Pack 1)</span>
